data.description: CHECK OUT THIS GREAT NEW PRICE! Priced to sell, 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled on a generous .58 acre lot in the city limits. Perfect for first-time buyers, investors, or those seeking a peaceful mountain getaway. Conveniently located 1 mile from the vibrant Lumber Arts District, you'll have easy access to an array of dining, music, and art experiences. This property combines the best of both worlds – a private, country setting just minutes away from Main Street Brevard. This affordable, manufactured home boasts an open floor plan with split bedrooms. With no restrictions, feel free to bring your chickens and embrace the homestead lifestyle. The large concrete drive offers easy access and plenty of parking for you and your guests.
